# Growvisi API product rules

## Tenant scope

Every query/mutation scoped by `organizationId` from JWT. Never leak cross-org data.

## Entitlements

Call `EntitlementsService` before:
- Adding WhatsApp numbers
- Inviting members
- AI classify (`assertHasAccess`)
- API key creation (Pro + active)

Return `402 Payment Required` with `TRIAL_EXPIRED` / `SUBSCRIPTION_INACTIVE` codes.

## Webhooks

WhatsApp + Razorpay: verify signatures in production (`isProductionDeploy()`). Fail closed if secret missing.

## AI boundaries

- `ai-classify`: updates stage/score; creates `AiRun` + timeline events
- `suggest-reply`: draft text only; inject `knowledgeDocument.rawContent`; never auto-send
- Do not add `AI_RESPOND` or auto-outbound to customers without explicit PRD change

## Automations

Email-only for v1 alerts (hot lead, follow-up). Log auditable metadata on conversation for timeline.

## Billing

Razorpay only. Plan IDs: `trial`, `starter`, `growth`, `pro`. Shared limits in `@growvisi/shared/billing`.

## New endpoints checklist

- [ ] JwtAuthGuard + org scope
- [ ] Plan limit if resource-consuming
- [ ] DTOs declared **before** controller class (hoisting bug)
- [ ] Documented in PRD if user-facing
